ce for Palestinians, criticism of Israeli policies. For this, as far back as 2005:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rancourt.academicfreedom.ca/background/targetingadissident.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://rancourt.academicfreedom.ca/background/targetingadissident.html</a>\r\n\r\nWhen an academic or politician or anyone in a position with a public voice speaks anything contrary to the Zionist narrative, they are demonized. \r\n\r\nHis current case is clearly an unbalanced situation in which, due to the bias of the judge, Rancourt stands no chance of a fair hearing. \r\n\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Eva Bartlett","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21924415"},{"created_at":"2014-05-29T23:33:46Z","content":"I need justice like clean water","like_count":0,"author_name":"Frigga Karl","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2205305"},{"created_at":"2014-05-25T14:35:42Z","content":"This case looks like bullfighting. A defenseless man is cynically put to death in the arenas of justice. It recalls the Dreyfus Affair in France. On behalf of Voltaire: \"J'accuse ...\"","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sa\u00efd Boukendour","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/100687195"},{"created_at":"2014-05-23T00:06:12Z","content":"Academic freedom","like_count":0,"author_name":"Alain Desroches","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/99474250"},{"created_at":"2014-05-23T16:01:59Z","content":"Why was the legal defence cancelled at the last minute, after it was allowed and had been studied in detail for three years? Please, no more gagging of academics. Period.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Nadia Abu-Zahra","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23505705"},{"created_at":"2014-05-26T11:24:38Z","content":"Brave person being politically   persecuted,so wrongly,  Let real justice prevail.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amy Harlib","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/106377"},{"created_at":"2014-05-22T13:28:41Z","content":"OCLA's campaign about this case: \"Public Money is Not for Silencing Critics\" <a href=\"http://ocla.ca/our-work/public-campaigns/public-money-is-not-for-silencing-critics/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://ocla.ca/our-work/public-campaigns/public-money-is-not-for-silencing-critics/</a>","like_count":0,"author_name":"Joseph Hickey","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3472027"},{"created_at":"2014-05-30T20:36:16Z","content":"Since our Charter does not specifically address our right to freedom of speech, it is up to a clearly unbiased judicial system to uphold our right to free speech...  in this case, Judge Charles Hackland does not meet this most basic criteria, so I join other petitioners in requesting a thorough review of the proceedings.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michael Graham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/11403646"},{"created_at":"2014-05-30T00:42:05Z","content":"As a former pro se litigant, I know well the experience of having one's case quashed by the court.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gerald Rubin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1822305"},{"created_at":"2014-05-29T14:17:15Z","content":"Justice is always important","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kemberly Martin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57007577"},{"created_at":"2014-05-25T02:01:59Z","content":"Injustice for one threatens justice for all","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brian Farrell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/53577543"},{"created_at":"2014-05-25T14:59:11Z","content":"Rancourt has taken the idea of justice to its actual end, exposing the fascist network of university administrator henchmen and a fermented legal system. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"Gordon Shean","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/80672259"},{"created_at":"2014-05-24T22:09:47Z","content":"because I believe in freedom of speech and equal rights","like_count":0,"author_name":"PATRICIA  WELLS","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/1489176"},{"created_at":"2014-05-22T16:15:59Z","content":"Judges in a position of conflict-of-interest should recuse themselves, not make flagrant rulings that comprise any notions of a fair trial.","like_count":0,"author_name":"greg macdougall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/3274930"},{"created_at":"2014-05-22T12:23:51Z","content":"I am signing this petition  to do something to counter the personally witnessed considerably wider (corporate) systemic multi-level occlusion of context as a weapon of destruction of academic freedom.\r\n\u201cIf you want to tell people the truth, make them laugh, otherwise they'll kill you.\u201d (O Wilde? GB Shaw?)\r\n","like_count":0,"author_name":"Claude Lamontagne","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/99088160"},{"created_at":"2014-05-29T17:02:27Z","content":"This isn't the first time a Canadian judge has skewed justice by disallowing the legal defence:\r\n\r\nThe UsuryFree Eye Opener: The Day Free Speech Died In Canada \u2013 October 2, 2013\r\n<a href=\"http://usuryfree.blogspot.ca/2013/10/the-day-free-speech-died-in-canada.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://usuryfree.blogspot.ca/2013/10/the-day-free-speech-died-in-canada.html</a>","like_count":0,"author_name":"John Bovay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/2002900"},{"created_at":"2014-05-29T12:29:24Z","content":"This seems a clear case where recusal by the judge was required.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Liz Wally","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/321567"},{"created_at":"2014-05-29T06:25:29Z","content":"Give justice to Prof Denis Rancourt","like_count":0,"author_name":"Binu Mathew","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/32615465"},{"created_at":"2014-05-24T18:26:34Z","content":"because i lkie to speak my, especially when i know im speaking the truth, but i have had the same problem, prosecuted for free truthful speaking.","like_count":0,"author_name":"JOHN A. WALKER 3rd","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/100409065"},{"created_at":"2014-05-30T02:05:00Z","content":"An injustice anywhere is an injustice everywhere...","like_count":0,"author_name":"Charles Atkinson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/10477922"